              <span id="reviewTextContainer953174426" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2271401572712202206">A riveting dramatic story consisting of a heart-wrenching and much to realistic story. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22221083.Honor_and_Polygamy' title='Honor and Polygamy by Omar Farhad' rel='nofollow noopener'>Honor and Polygamy</a> truly captivated me in its engrossing plot. A definite page turner, author Farhad has a compelling voice throughout that remains with the reader long after reading. Read it, but expect some tears and controversy. An incredible point of view in the political field. </span>
  <span id="freeText2271401572712202206" style="display:none">A riveting dramatic story consisting of a heart-wrenching and much to realistic story. <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22221083.Honor_and_Polygamy" title="Honor and Polygamy by Omar Farhad" rel="nofollow noopener">Honor and Polygamy</a> truly captivated me in its engrossing plot. A definite page turner, author Farhad has a compelling voice throughout that remains with the reader long after reading. Read it, but expect some tears and controversy. An incredible point of view in the political field. </span>
